2. If this ſhould be a good Releaſe, it diſcharges only ſuch Actions which he hath in his own Right; for by the words all Actions which he had are releaſed;
                  Cro. Eliz. 6. 1 Leon. 263. 
                  now if an Executor grant omnia bona ſua, the Goods which he hath as Executor do not paſs.

